{
  "stem": "18575.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every time there was a British Air Force bomb Berlin at night, and-- [CLEARS THROAT] --they would come first in, I think, fighter planes or spotter planes and drop what we call Christmas trees spotting phosphor of different colors.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And look like a, like a Christmas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Giant, colorful thing hanging in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was markers for the bombers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then came the bombers and bomb, and the earth shook.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we had to run out, out of the barracks, and lay on the ground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was fantastic, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Watching Berlin being bombed, when we are right next to it, and the earth shaking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Americans-- [CLEARS THROAT] --bombed that in the daytime, but you didn't see the flares and all these things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed until April.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian were advanced on, on Berlin, and we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We evacuated-- we are, we are evacuated by foot with no food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A march.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, if you didn't make it, you're dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're marching along the road on the side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And tens of thousands of prisoners from different concentration camps were marching on the road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German army was marching in the middle of the road in either direction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This arranged the soldiers unshaved, not the glorious, victorious supermen, but beaten, running in all directions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the American P-51's used to fly over and machine gun them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if they saw a prison colony like ours, they used to fly right over us and gun in front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And many times they would kill horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And by the time our column went by a dead horse, there was nothing left but a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We used to cut the meat away.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
